sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Data Science Gateway<br/>(Envoy) 443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAuth as Kubernetes API<br/>(SubjectAccessReview)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as model-registry REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (loopback)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Model Registry REST API Request (Gateway API Path)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /model-registry/{name}/...<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Gateway->>KRP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS (serving cert)<br/>X-Forwarded headers
        KRP->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAuth-->>KRP: Authorized (user has get on services/{name})
        KRP->>Registry: Forward (localhost)<br/>HTTP (loopback, pre-authorized)
        Registry->>PG: SQL query<br/>PostgreSQL protocol<br/>Optional TLS (client certs)<br/>Password auth
        PG-->>Registry: Query result
        Registry-->>KRP: JSON response
        KRP-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 2: Model Registry REST API Request (OpenShift Route Path)
        Client->>Router: POST /{name}-rest.{domain}/...<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Router->>KRP: Re-encrypt<br/>HTTPS TLS (re-encrypt)<br/>X-Forwarded headers
        KRP->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAuth-->>KRP: Authorized
        KRP->>Registry: Forward (localhost)<br/>HTTP (loopback, pre-authorized)
        Registry->>PG: SQL query<br/>Password auth
        PG-->>Registry: Query result
        Registry-->>KRP: JSON response
        KRP-->>Router: HTTPS response
        Router-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    participant MigMgr as StorageMigrationManager
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 230, 255)
        Note over MigMgr,K8sAPI: Flow 3: CRD Storage Version Migration
        MigMgr->>K8sAPI: Check CRD storedVersions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>MigMgr: CRD status (has v1alpha1)
        alt SVM Strategy
            MigMgr->>K8sAPI: Create StorageVersionMigration CR
            K8sAPI-->>MigMgr: Migration progress/completion
        else Manual Strategy
            MigMgr->>K8sAPI: List all ModelRegistry CRs
            K8sAPI-->>MigMgr: CR list
            loop For each CR
                MigMgr->>K8sAPI: Re-read and re-write CR<br/>(triggers storage version update)
            end
        end
        MigMgr->>K8sAPI: Patch CRD storedVersions<br/>(remove v1alpha1)
    end
